eb1f71e0-d5ae-42a4-b43d-4c48c1899acd.title: Essence Mascara Lash Princess
eb1f71e0-d5ae-42a4-b43d-4c48c1899acd.description: The Essence Mascara Lash Princess is a popular mascara known for its volumizing and lengthening effects. Achieve dramatic lashes with this long-lasting and cruelty-free formula.

968a8ba8-f4e1-492d-9172-00e276efd4e0.title: Eyeshadow Palette with Mirror
968a8ba8-f4e1-492d-9172-00e276efd4e0.description: The Eyeshadow Palette with Mirror offers a versatile range of eyeshadow shades for creating stunning eye looks. With a built-in mirror, it's convenient for on-the-go makeup application.

c6076acf-2398-4ea0-89f5-6a5fe8e5a222.title: Powder Canister
c6076acf-2398-4ea0-89f5-6a5fe8e5a222.description: The Powder Canister is a finely milled setting powder designed to set makeup and control shine. With a lightweight and translucent formula, it provides a smooth and matte finish.

ed800a70-6818-4a47-ab60-a117974ff7aa.title: Red Lipstick
ed800a70-6818-4a47-ab60-a117974ff7aa.description: The Red Lipstick is a classic and bold choice for adding a pop of color to your lips. With a creamy and pigmented formula, it provides a vibrant and long-lasting finish.

5937e60f-c9aa-4142-8b64-06e797e9ddf3.title: Red Nail Polish
5937e60f-c9aa-4142-8b64-06e797e9ddf3.description: The Red Nail Polish offers a rich and glossy red hue for vibrant and polished nails. With a quick-drying formula, it provides a salon-quality finish at home.

28bcf22c-23f6-4cab-8127-173a953ebd1d.title: Calvin Klein CK One
28bcf22c-23f6-4cab-8127-173a953ebd1d.description: CK One by Calvin Klein is a classic unisex fragrance, known for its fresh and clean scent. It's a versatile fragrance suitable for everyday wear.

58265e58-6b83-4174-aff3-41aef8a1d0f7.title: Chanel Coco Noir Eau De
58265e58-6b83-4174-aff3-41aef8a1d0f7.description: Coco Noir by Chanel is an elegant and mysterious fragrance, featuring notes of grapefruit, rose, and sandalwood. Perfect for evening occasions.

45868fbb-26c3-428d-a65d-998ae9c28808.title: Dior J'adore
45868fbb-26c3-428d-a65d-998ae9c28808.description: J'adore by Dior is a luxurious and floral fragrance, known for its blend of ylang-ylang, rose, and jasmine. It embodies femininity and sophistication.
